<body>

  <!-- Header with Home button -->
  <header class="terms-header">
    <h1>TickOrder - Shipping Policy</h1>
    <a href="index.html" class="back-home-btn">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-house"></i>
    </a>
  </header>

  <main style="padding: 20px; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; line-height: 1.6;">

    <section>
      <h2>1. Shipping Areas</h2>
      <p>
        TickOrder delivers to locations within South Africa. For areas outside our delivery zones, please contact us directly to confirm availability.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>2. Processing Time</h2>
      <p>
        All orders are processed within <strong>1–2 business days</strong> after payment confirmation. Orders placed on weekends or public holidays will be processed the next business day.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>3. Delivery Time</h2>
      <p>
        Standard delivery usually takes <strong>2–5 business days</strong> depending on your location. While we strive to deliver within this time, delays may occur due to unforeseen circumstances such as weather or courier delays.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>4. Shipping Fees</h2>
      <p>
        Shipping fees are calculated at checkout based on the delivery location and weight of the order. Any applicable fees will be displayed before payment is completed.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>5. Tracking Orders</h2>
      <p>
        Once your order is shipped, you will receive a tracking number via email or SMS. You can use this number to monitor the progress of your delivery.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>6. Lost or Damaged Packages</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Please inspect your package upon delivery.</li>
        <li>If your package is lost or damaged, contact TickOrder immediately at <strong>tickorderstore@gmail.com</strong> or <strong>0766506107</strong>.</li>
        <li>We will assist in filing a claim with the courier and arrange a replacement if applicable.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        For any shipping questions, contact us at <strong>tickorderstore@gmail.com</strong> or call <strong>0766506107</strong>.
      </p>
    </section>

  </main>

